# DSK fixture (minimal)

This directory contains a small DSK (Digital Shape Kernel) used by tests.

## Provenance

- Source directory (NAIF): https://naif.jpl.nasa.gov/pub/naif/ORX/kernels/dsk/
- File: `apophis_g_25000mm_rad_obj_0000n00000_v001.bds`
